{"tid":2517360,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"免費樣本收集包淪炒賣 收「代取費」每個25蚊","createTime":"2021-05-05T09:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T10:31:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e82a9c01469343973839b240586ee125f06711ed","tid":2517360,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:19:57.000Z","msg":"變種病毒襲港，加上各行各業須定期強檢，深喉唾液樣本收集包供不應求，卻疑被人藉此圖利。有人於拍賣網上販售樣本包，收取每個約25元的「代取費」，部份賣家更聲稱有「存貨」，可預約於港鐵站交收或郵寄送貨。食衞局回覆，最近數周收回的樣本包約為派發量的一半，呼籲市民毋須過度索取樣本包，更不應轉售圖利。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210505/4MANYECQABAO3LQN73A5PFULDM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210505%2F4MANYECQABAO3LQN73A5PFULDM%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=34f1c55b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210505%2F4MANYECQABAO3LQN73A5PFULDM%2F&h=07f51564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210505/4MANYECQABAO3LQN73A5PFULDM/</a>"},{"pid":"9f559d23d030c1fe79f9df19c9ea53512dc1dc90","tid":2517360,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7b86ea0db585b143ec096296c5a27a5ae85d9eda","tid":2517360,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"乜鳩都炒一餐"},{"pid":"a7b12673631f96e99d64a61e0ac9a940f4e32849","tid":2517360,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:09:09.000Z","msg":"淘寶山寨到呢D收集包未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2ed1ffdb96a68a94146ede946edc9c57119fa9","tid":2517360,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:11:50.000Z","msg":"更加顯得政府on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e69b5fd211dda16aaba3ce2468fcc7fc490dcf","tid":2517360,"uid":60202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":